    "• Choose a model that is more accurate altogether after making a few tweaks.There will constantly be improved algorithms, thus users should really not waste their time fine-tuning deep learning models.",
    "Forming a realistic assumption of precision is aided by investigating the data.",
    "To set goals to beat, start with straightforward linear tactics.",
    "Various deep learning algorithms could be more useful, quick, and efficient than your initial choice [366][367][368].",
